Package com.dev.sweproject

Class ByteArrayMultipartFile

java.lang.Object
com.dev.sweproject.ByteArrayMultipartFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.core.io.InputStreamSource, org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile
public class ByteArrayMultipartFile extends Object implements org.springframework.web.multipart.MultipartFile
The ByteArrayMultipart class represents a component for encapsulating the properties of a file in memory as a byte array. It implements the MultipartFile interface, providing convenient methods for handling and processing file data. This class is designed to facilitate in-memory manipulation of file-like data.
